100g room temperature butter
100g caster sugar
1 medium egg
1 tsp vanilla extract
275g plain flour



preheat oven to 170C
slightly mix the vanilla into the egg
cream together the butter and sugar
mix the egg in stages
stir in the flour to form a dough
roll out to 1 cm thick on a floured worktop
cooookie cutter
bake for 8-10 min, cool for at least 2 min on the tray before transferring to a wire rack

